# See https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore for syntax details.

### Dependencies ###
# Ignore local dependency directories.
/node_modules

### Build Artifacts ###
# Ignore compiled files, build caches, and other artifacts.
/dist
/.tsbuildinfo
*.tsbuildinfo

### Bun ###
# The binary lockfile can cause merge conflicts across different OSs.
# It's regenerated by `bun install`, so it's safe to ignore.
bun.lockb

### Logs ###
# Ignore log files from various package managers.
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

### Local Environment ###
# Ignore sensitive environment variables and local-only config files.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

### Operating System ###
# Ignore files generated by macOS, Windows, and other OS-level tools.
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

### Editor / IDE ###
# The .vscode directory is intentionally versioned. It contains shared project
# settings and extension recommendations to ensure a consistent development
# environment for all collaborators.
